<div id="wiki-tab-0-3" style="display:none">
<p>Items I've made as the primary graphic designer for the Amino. If you don't know what the SCP Amino is, I don't blame you. It's a fandom app meant for the younger side of the community, aged between 13-16. There's a lot of OCs and RPs and whatnot there, but consider it a place where people enjoy the fandom and learn and grow. Think of it as SCP preschool in a way. If you don't like the off-site community, I get it, but I would argue it's best for them to have a space off of the Wiki to enjoy the fandom how they best see fit than have them here on the Wiki when they're not quite ready yet.<br />
<br />
I more or less own the place now, and run it with the rest of my staff team. If you have any further questions about the place, feel free to reach out! I'm happy to sit down and chat and clear up any misconceptions about the place folks might have. But hey, if it is not your thing, feel free to not come near it with a ten foot pole haha.</p>
